data.description: Price improvement! Room to grow in Spring Hill! This home features a huge great room with a vaulted ceiling and gorgeous fireplace, perfect for entertaining and relaxing. The desirable split 3/2 floor plan also includes spacious dining room, eat-in kitchen and roomy screened lanai that expands the living space outdoors. Perfect for experienced renovators, or for anyone ready to make their home owning dreams become reality.     Located on a quiet, established street, this property offers a peaceful retreat while still being conveniently close to shopping, restaurants, amenities, and area attractions. Just a short commute to the Tampa area! Cash offers or renovation loans with 0 inspection days only considered. All information recorded in the MLS is intended to be accurate but cannot be guaranteed, buyer advised to verify. Sold As-Is.
